SMS changed to MMS when moving from iPhone to Android
text: I took the text message backup from my iPhone. Most of these text messages were simple SMS which companies send when you buy something online e.g. "Thx you for shopping, you spent 3$ here.." When I moved these SMS to my android (Samsung), all of them show as MMS on android. Any clue why its so?
